Summary: saw 1 stationary pulsating multi colored object then was joined by another I took a couple photos and during the review I noticed a 3rd disc shaped object
divs: Sighting Details Driving down Hwy 53 in watkinsville going west toward Hwy 78 we noticed a bright multi colored pulsating light we pulled over to get a picture and noticed 1 more appeared. I took a couple more pics then we tried to relocate due to street lights obstructing our view.We searched but they were gone. Upon review I see a third cigar object, which I thought was a cloud,apparently it is something worth looking at I will send these new pics asap
